  "original_title": "\u2019\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc7\u0ba9\u0bcd\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'I will not be unfaithful'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa said that he has never betrayed the empty face protest and that position will not change in the future.",
        "A special meeting between the representatives representing the Khali Mukhatidal protest field and the opposition leader Sajith Premadasa was held at the opposition leader's office in Colombo yesterday (18th) morning.",
        "Tomorrow (20th) as the poll to elect the interim president will be held, the representatives of the Khalimaguthidal protest field met the leader of the opposition Sajith Premadasa and expressed their position.",
        "During this, the leader of the opposition party said that he, his party or his alliance would never betray the demands of the protest, and said that neither he nor his party or his alliance would ever betray the demands of the protest and said that they will not be betrayed in the future."
      ],
